Penne Rosa

1 box (1 lb.) Penne pasta
1 T white wine
2 T olive oil
1/2 cup marinara sauce
1/4 cup sliced mushrooms (canned, drained or fresh)
1 (14 oz.) can Italian -style diced tomatoes
1/2 tsp. ground or crushed red pepper

1/4 cup heavy cream
1/4 cup fresh spinach, packed
Grilled chicken breast, sauteed shrimp or asparagus
Fresh grated Parmesan cheese

Boil pasta according to package directions; set aside.
In a large skillet, heat wine, oil, marinara, mushrooms, tomatoes and red
pepper over medium heat; stir liberally for 4-5 minutes. Add pasta, mixing
well. Add cream and continue stirring. Fold in spinach, stirring until wilted.
Stir in cooked chicken, shrimp or asparagus. Serve with fresh Parmesan on top.
